buildIdeas.title: Audius Royalty Split Automation Engine
buildIdeas.description: Build a smart contract system that automatically distributes streaming royalties to multiple artists, producers, and labels based on pre-configured splits, settling in real-time on Solana. This capitalizes on Audius's protocol acceleration by enabling complex revenue sharing that current music platforms struggle with.
buildIdeas.whyNow: Audius's 23 commits signal active protocol development. Artists on Audius need trustless royalty distribution; building this now positions you to integrate as Audius scales user adoption.

buildIdeas.title: Firedancer Performance Monitoring Dashboard

buildIdeas.whyNow: Firedancer is gaining +3 stars (highest momentum). Validators need transparent performance data to justify client switching; this tool removes adoption friction.

buildIdeas.title: BisonFi Liquidity Aggregator with MEV Protection
buildIdeas.description: Build a swap router that aggregates liquidity across BisonFi, Orca, and Raydium while using Jito's MEV protection to minimize slippage and sandwich attacks. Route trades to BisonFi when it offers best execution, capturing the volume surge.
buildIdeas.whyNow: BisonFi's +20.96% volume delta (3.95 z-score) shows market share capture. Building MEV-protected routing now captures traders migrating from PumpSwap while BisonFi momentum peaks.

buildIdeas.title: DEX Volume Arbitrage Monitor & Alert System

buildIdeas.whyNow: PumpSwap's -37.4% volume decline creates arbitrage opportunities as traders migrate. Real-time alerts capture the window before market equilibrates.
